.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-CAPACITY-KURTOSIS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-capacity-kurtosis \- FEAT-2848 peer-capacity-kurtosis
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-capacity-kurtosis
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the excess kurtosis of total capacity (msat) aggregated per peer for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2848).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBcapacity_kurtosis_peer\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
